        "subject": "LU-615 lprocfs: redo 'import' proc file with seq_file",
        "message": "LU-615 lprocfs: redo 'import' proc file with seq_file\n\nThe 'import' data may be quite big but current implementation of\nlprocfs_rd_import() will cut output data at the end of buffer.\nPatch switch import data read/write to the using seq_file interface\nwhich solve this problem.\n\nAdditional fixes in patch are about error handling in osc_setup,\nmdc_setup and mgc_setup. All were made in similar manner.\n\nChange-Id: Ica7fd743f2a6d6f0c44e5f75316d9714594eb3fc\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <tappro@whamcloud.com>\n"
